Tawaten piiqnaaghtusi ineghhnemsi, elpekqun naagpek, atagpek mengyaghlleqiinkuti!"
Yulqusighllaget anglikat angtaniitkat, sangwaa allaaghhiinaq tawaten ineghneghlliqut neghyukluku uteghhnaluki taghnughhateng, pingulghiit.
Wetku tawatenginaq piyaghqaanayukata.

Qineghsaghtughyalghiimi ii-uka.
"Heng, wata araghtegaa, qenwatlu taakwa piqaghhnaqiisi, legan tawaten pilleghmitun piqaghnaqiisi."
Elngaatall, Meregtemiinguut tazimanirugllak Meregtem yugwa.
